# DunderIA sensitive-area ownership map.
#
# Replace @nex-crm/dunderia-maintainers with the real GitHub team/user before
# enforcing branch protection. The patterns are intentionally scoped to areas
# where a small accidental change can affect releases, credentials, topology,
# runtime safety, or public packaging.

